<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4900735>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 13. Proximal end of the left tarsometatarsus of Physornis fortis (MACN-A-52-185) in views: A - proximal, B - medial, C - dorsal, D - lateral and E - plantar. This specimen appears to be associated to the fragment of mandibular symphysis (MACN-A-52-186) and served as type for Aucornis euryrhynchus Ameghino, 1899." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4900735/files/figure.png" .

